426
00:32:09.067 --> 00:32:10.853
<i>♪ How come you are striking me? ♪</i>

427
00:32:10.985 --> 00:32:16.597
<i>♪ Without a knife
And without making me bleed ♪</i>

428
00:32:16.731 --> 00:32:22.282
